# .trivyignore — Trivy finding suppressions for tf-modules
#
# Format: one AVD/CVE ID per line, with a comment explaining why it's suppressed.
# Example:
#   AVD-AWS-0086  # S3 bucket: access logging not required for this ephemeral scratch bucket
#
# See https://aquasecurity.github.io/trivy/latest/docs/configuration/filtering/#trivyignore
#
# This file is intentionally empty — all current HIGH/CRITICAL findings must be fixed.
